<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="race-n">race <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /reɪs/    美 /reɪs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 种族；人种：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Our nation welcomes people of all races, colors, and religions. 
我们国家欢迎不同种族、肤色和宗教信仰的人。</p></div>

<h4 id="2c">2.<strong>[C] (生物的) 种；属；类：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>The human race</strong> is using up Earth’s resources. 
人类正在逐渐用尽地球的资源。</p><footer>译林⑤ – 3</footer></div></div>